WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
ظآزThat dayظآز

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
ظآزNothing stays together foreverظآز

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
ظآزI've quit romanceظآز

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
ظآزWho hasn't failed againظآز

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
ظآزCrying in deathظآز

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
ظآزAnd in lifeظآز

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
ظآزEven nowظآز

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
ظآزWe keep learningظآز

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
ظآزIt's no surpriseظآز

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
ظآزBeing happy is so hardظآز

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
ظآزWeirdly, I became a role modelظآز

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
ظآزOn the day we met again, we said hiظآز

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
ظآزIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintظآز

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
ظآزWho can do anything without regretظآز

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
ظآزI am all rightظآز

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
ظآزMay you live in peaceظآز

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
ظآزLet the world roarظآز

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
ظآزSounds like a carnivalظآز

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
ظآزBeing alive is never dullظآز

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
ظآزHow wonderful to be freeظآز

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
ظآزI became even better without youظآز

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
ظآزNothing can be perfectظآز

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
ظآزWe bless each other in painظآز

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
ظآزWe nod and smileظآز

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
ظآزMay we both be wellظآز

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.898
=Episode 18=

01:48.304 --> 01:48.904
Xu.

01:49.863 --> 01:51.343
Have a seat.

01:52.584 --> 01:53.063
Here.

01:56.584 --> 01:57.223
Sit here.

02:01.944 --> 02:03.423
An incognito visit?

02:08.304 --> 02:08.744
Well,

02:08.744 --> 02:09.744
that outdoor event

02:10.063 --> 02:11.264
was a huge success.

02:11.503 --> 02:12.543
The clients loved it.

02:14.663 --> 02:17.103
Why didn't you mention

02:17.304 --> 02:18.744
your influence at all?

02:22.063 --> 02:24.103
I know who your mother-in-law is.

02:25.264 --> 02:26.584
With your ability,

02:27.063 --> 02:29.063
you could ask her
to promote our products.

02:29.783 --> 02:32.904
I'll assign you
our luxury women's fashion brands.

02:33.584 --> 02:37.304
As long as your mother-in-law
and her CEO friends

02:37.424 --> 02:38.704
wear our clothes on camera,

02:38.864 --> 02:39.864
our sales

02:39.943 --> 02:41.343
will definitely skyrocket.

02:43.063 --> 02:44.103
Sorry, Mr. Qiu.

02:44.223 --> 02:45.063
It's not appropriate.

02:46.783 --> 02:48.024
Well, I understand.

02:48.343 --> 02:49.343
They can't show up, huh?

02:50.223 --> 02:51.223
But you can do it.

02:51.704 --> 02:55.144
You can build yourself
into a classy socialite persona.

02:55.543 --> 02:57.063
Talk about your world.

02:57.584 --> 02:58.304
Like...

02:59.223 --> 03:00.503
How to marry into wealth.

03:01.024 --> 03:03.503
How to fend off mistresses.

03:03.783 --> 03:04.704
Marriage wars,

03:04.744 --> 03:05.904
splitting assets,

03:06.103 --> 03:07.623
fights with rich in-laws,

03:07.663 --> 03:08.704
and so on.

03:08.864 --> 03:10.503
Share those stories,

03:10.623 --> 03:11.304
and I swear

03:11.824 --> 03:13.124
you'll gain followers instantly.

03:16.943 --> 03:17.864
I'm not doing that.

03:22.984 --> 03:23.503
Fine.

03:25.464 --> 03:26.184
Okay.

03:26.744 --> 03:27.503
You may leave now.

03:37.543 --> 03:38.103
Mr. Qiu.

03:38.264 --> 03:38.943
What?

03:41.304 --> 03:42.704
It's the end of the month,

03:43.223 --> 03:45.503
and I still haven't been paid.

03:46.744 --> 03:48.024
I want to ask...

03:48.584 --> 03:49.584
Could you...?

03:54.584 --> 03:55.024
Okay.

03:57.503 --> 03:58.543
Let me check.

03:58.704 --> 03:59.223
Thank you.

04:03.984 --> 04:04.783
Last week...

04:05.488 --> 04:08.368
(Payout of live stream anchors)

04:09.223 --> 04:10.024
20,000 in total.

04:11.024 --> 04:11.904
Thank you, Mr. Qiu.

04:12.184 --> 04:15.343
But the warm-up host,

04:15.904 --> 04:17.983
IT team for product
listing and unlisting,

04:18.343 --> 04:19.464
sales, customer service,

04:19.504 --> 04:20.863
and product sourcing,

04:20.983 --> 04:23.624
all that gets deducted.

04:24.783 --> 04:27.303
Let me recalculate your balance.

04:30.512 --> 04:32.048
(Payout of live stream anchors)

04:33.343 --> 04:34.423
You've got 1,400 left.

04:42.704 --> 04:44.584
Can I see the breakdown?

04:45.863 --> 04:47.024
I don't think that's fair.

04:48.743 --> 04:49.504
Want more money?

04:50.303 --> 04:51.343
Then do what I said.

04:52.183 --> 04:53.343
Just spin a story.

04:54.183 --> 04:55.064
Like...

04:55.504 --> 04:57.904
A career woman marrying into wealth

04:58.103 --> 05:00.663
and making it her own.

05:01.504 --> 05:02.944
Very inspiring.

05:03.223 --> 05:05.384
You'd be a top influencer in no time.

05:06.464 --> 05:09.223
The daily commission

05:09.303 --> 05:10.904
would beat your yearly salary.

05:11.343 --> 05:13.343
At that time, no more swallowing pride.

05:18.944 --> 05:19.983
Please email me

05:20.624 --> 05:21.743
the breakdown.

05:23.303 --> 05:24.024
I quit.

05:28.624 --> 05:30.381
ظآزWhere does the soul come fromظآز

05:30.381 --> 05:32.235
ظآزAn island of exile for dreamsظآز

05:32.624 --> 05:34.743
What a waste of a hot topic.

05:35.904 --> 05:36.423
Idiot.

05:38.137 --> 05:39.914
ظآزI'm ready to shineظآز

05:39.914 --> 05:41.872
ظآزReproductions may dazzleظآز

05:41.872 --> 05:43.760
ظآزBut living uniquely outshinesظآز

05:44.303 --> 05:46.264
Two bottles left.

05:48.343 --> 05:50.863
I've put the milk
and yogurt in the fridge

05:51.064 --> 05:52.504
and thrown away the expired ones.

05:53.423 --> 05:54.183
Okay.

05:54.743 --> 05:56.423
I love those promo freebies.

05:57.456 --> 05:58.928
ظآزConfidence shapes my styleظآز

05:59.303 --> 06:00.863
You survive on snacks all day,

06:01.303 --> 06:02.704
never eat proper meals.

06:04.983 --> 06:06.863
Here,

06:06.904 --> 06:07.904
fruit and cookies.

06:08.543 --> 06:10.464
Thank you, Xu. You're so sweet.

06:12.976 --> 06:14.576
ظآزI'm ready to shineظآز

06:16.103 --> 06:17.743
What are you doing?

06:18.343 --> 06:20.944
Maximizing the leftover value.

06:26.992 --> 06:28.600
(Trial product)

06:31.504 --> 06:33.384
These trial bottles were used by many.

06:33.504 --> 06:35.983
It's not clean. Don't...

06:36.423 --> 06:37.863
You know how much it costs?

06:38.024 --> 06:39.024
This way,

06:39.064 --> 06:40.423
I can get half a bottle more.

06:40.663 --> 06:41.464
I don't mind.

06:42.584 --> 06:43.863
If you really...

06:44.024 --> 06:44.624
It's fine.

06:45.103 --> 06:46.064
Can you hold it for me?

06:49.103 --> 06:50.504
Stop using this, seriously.

06:50.663 --> 06:51.343
It's okay.

06:51.343 --> 06:52.704
Answer it on speaker.

06:53.628 --> 06:55.103
(Guan)

06:55.103 --> 06:56.423
Hello? What's up?

06:57.024 --> 06:57.663
Qiao Lin.

06:57.863 --> 06:59.423
Yao's competition results are out.

06:59.743 --> 07:00.303
How'd she do?

07:00.543 --> 07:01.384
Not great.

07:01.584 --> 07:02.824
She's really upset now.

07:03.064 --> 07:04.904
Can you come cheer her up?

07:04.983 --> 07:05.663
Of course.

07:05.663 --> 07:06.464
I'll be right there.

07:06.584 --> 07:07.183
I'll hang up.

07:09.303 --> 07:10.423
You're free, right?

07:10.944 --> 07:12.024
Why not go with me?

07:12.183 --> 07:13.584
I'll introduce you.

07:14.704 --> 07:15.824
But she's in a bad mood...

07:15.824 --> 07:16.543
It's not...

07:16.543 --> 07:17.824
It's appropriate. Really.

07:18.024 --> 07:18.944
I'll get changed.

07:20.024 --> 07:21.144
Then... I'll pack these up.

07:21.183 --> 07:21.743
Go ahead.

07:33.303 --> 07:38.983
This is the most stunning
ethnic-style outfit I've ever seen.

07:40.183 --> 07:40.663
Yao,

07:40.904 --> 07:42.783
you're really talented in design.

07:43.384 --> 07:44.584
Don't be discouraged.

07:44.663 --> 07:46.264
One contest doesn't mean much.

07:46.584 --> 07:47.743
You'll do better next time.

07:50.103 --> 07:51.504
You already did great.

07:51.543 --> 07:53.343
That was a national contest.

07:53.343 --> 07:54.343
That's impressive.

07:55.144 --> 07:55.904
Right.

07:57.584 --> 07:58.944
Got knocked out in the semifinals.

07:59.743 --> 08:00.663
Don't lose hope.

08:00.783 --> 08:01.904
Just work harder

08:02.064 --> 08:03.423
and try again.

08:04.064 --> 08:04.584
Exactly.

08:04.783 --> 08:08.423
I noticed your sketches and final pieces
weren't fully matched.

08:08.584 --> 08:10.103
Many accessories missing.

08:10.423 --> 08:11.983
If it's due to time constraints,

08:12.103 --> 08:13.624
you'll do better next time

08:13.624 --> 08:14.504
with enough time.

08:15.584 --> 08:16.663
It's not about time.

08:18.423 --> 08:19.223
It's about money.

08:27.103 --> 08:29.863
Fashion design burns money.

08:30.464 --> 08:31.663
Fabric's expensive,

08:31.743 --> 08:33.024
and accessories too.

08:34.183 --> 08:36.504
Hiring models, shooting photos,
all cost.

08:40.303 --> 08:41.423
When I delivered takeout,

08:41.423 --> 08:42.264
I kept thinking

08:43.504 --> 08:45.823
that after 100 orders

08:46.224 --> 08:48.303
I'll buy those fabrics.

08:48.624 --> 08:51.024
After 500

08:51.344 --> 08:53.423
I'll afford those buttons.

08:57.303 --> 08:59.344
People said I was dreaming,

09:01.104 --> 09:01.984
but I didn't care.

09:07.104 --> 09:10.264
After I finally saved up and entered,
I realized

09:11.703 --> 09:14.463
the costs would keep ballooning.

09:17.904 --> 09:19.224
Soon

09:20.864 --> 09:22.463
I can't even afford fabric.

09:26.624 --> 09:27.423
It's the truth.

09:27.984 --> 09:29.504
With my salary,

09:30.504 --> 09:31.583
after rent

09:31.783 --> 09:33.144
and basics,

09:33.303 --> 09:34.943
nothing's left.

09:35.224 --> 09:37.423
Earn and spend right away.

09:37.543 --> 09:38.943
Not a cent saved.

09:39.583 --> 09:41.864
People like us,

09:41.904 --> 09:43.224
shouldn't dream too big.

09:43.663 --> 09:46.183
Well... Just

09:46.423 --> 09:47.183
making ends meet

09:47.183 --> 09:48.423
is hard.

09:48.943 --> 09:49.463
Yao.

09:49.783 --> 09:52.543
Not everyone's dreams can come true.

09:52.783 --> 09:54.243
You can still design.

09:54.243 --> 09:55.224
Take it as a hobby.

09:55.823 --> 09:57.543
Don't push yourself so hard.

10:00.864 --> 10:01.423
No.

10:01.663 --> 10:02.744
No. No way.

10:02.984 --> 10:04.063
Like the movie says,

10:04.104 --> 10:06.344
without dreams, we're just salted fish.

10:08.183 --> 10:09.823
If 500 orders aren't enough,

10:10.104 --> 10:12.303
let's push for 600.

10:12.423 --> 10:14.183
We'll save enough.

10:14.264 --> 10:16.104
Just try it.

10:18.583 --> 10:20.423
It's so kind of you saying that.

10:22.423 --> 10:23.144
Alright.

10:23.783 --> 10:24.703
I've calculated.

10:25.224 --> 10:29.543
By the time I'm 120,
I'll have saved enough.

10:46.663 --> 10:47.984
Something on your mind?

10:53.144 --> 10:55.463
Seeing Guan just now

10:57.063 --> 10:59.864
reminded me
of my first years in Jingzhou.

11:00.663 --> 11:01.744
Just like them,

11:02.984 --> 11:04.904
I run around

11:06.463 --> 11:07.463
for survive.

11:08.583 --> 11:10.504
I was terrified

11:10.904 --> 11:13.783
one wrong move would cost me the city.

11:15.783 --> 11:21.823
So I desperately sought security.

11:28.264 --> 11:28.943
I know

11:31.264 --> 11:32.984
my way was wrong.

11:35.943 --> 11:37.943
But my goal wasn't.

11:39.624 --> 11:41.543
Wanting a quality life,

11:43.703 --> 11:45.943
creating better material condition
for my family,

11:50.183 --> 11:51.783
and changing my fate

11:54.943 --> 11:56.423
are not vanity.

11:58.703 --> 11:59.423
Of course.

12:00.104 --> 12:01.144
You're right.

12:02.224 --> 12:05.224
So we've got to work hard

12:05.504 --> 12:06.423
and to earn money.

12:08.583 --> 12:09.823
Living really costs.

12:18.183 --> 12:19.144
I want to try.

12:22.104 --> 12:22.583
What?

12:23.183 --> 12:23.864
You want to try?

12:24.463 --> 12:25.144
Try what?

12:31.543 --> 12:32.423
Paper copy's here.

12:32.703 --> 12:34.104
E-copy has been sent to your email.

12:35.024 --> 12:35.583
Thanks.

12:56.104 --> 12:56.703
Mr. Zhang.

12:59.423 --> 13:00.823
What's the plan now?

13:04.663 --> 13:06.024
Since I dared give it to him,

13:06.344 --> 13:08.104
there's nothing he can find.

13:11.344 --> 13:14.183
When Wang Defu comes back,

13:14.463 --> 13:17.624
inform him
about the headquarters' inspection team.

13:17.904 --> 13:18.543
Clever.

13:19.224 --> 13:21.044
Mr. Wu from Anqiang
ran off with his money.

13:21.144 --> 13:22.583
He's been trying to get it back.

13:23.144 --> 13:24.063
Let me tell you.

13:24.344 --> 13:26.104
That guy's trouble.

13:26.504 --> 13:27.063
Right.

13:27.624 --> 13:29.744
This is how we'll force him out.

13:34.063 --> 13:34.583
Mr. Shen.

13:34.864 --> 13:36.752
We just started
and they came causing trouble,

13:36.752 --> 13:37.840
preventing us from working.

13:38.024 --> 13:38.904
We tried reasoning,

13:38.984 --> 13:39.984
but they turned violent.

13:42.583 --> 13:43.264
Stop! Stop!

13:44.024 --> 13:44.583
Stop!

13:46.344 --> 13:47.144
What's going on?

13:47.904 --> 13:49.063
You're Mr. Shen, right?

13:53.943 --> 13:55.144
Let me introduce myself.

13:55.344 --> 13:55.904
I'm

13:56.183 --> 13:56.864
Wang Defu.

13:57.063 --> 13:58.583
Defu, as in 'virtue wins'.

13:58.943 --> 14:02.224
I heard you're here
to solve our problems.

14:02.303 --> 14:02.984
That's perfect.

14:03.303 --> 14:05.063
Jinda Group owes me six million.

14:05.423 --> 14:06.303
Pay up now.

14:06.823 --> 14:08.583
If I'm not mistaken,

14:09.024 --> 14:12.584
it was Wu Chengming from Anqiang

14:13.072 --> 14:15.423
who pulled you into this project, right?

14:15.744 --> 14:16.344
Exactly.

14:17.024 --> 14:18.624
It was a personal loan.

14:18.904 --> 14:20.543
Your loan agreement

14:20.984 --> 14:24.703
is between Anqiang Group and you.

14:24.904 --> 14:25.984
If you want repayment,

14:26.663 --> 14:28.904
go to Wu Chengming,

14:29.063 --> 14:30.063
not Jinda Group.

14:30.823 --> 14:33.663
Besides, police are already involved.

14:34.583 --> 14:38.303
He conned me using your project.

14:38.744 --> 14:40.423
Without Jinda Group's backing,

14:40.663 --> 14:42.104
he'd never dare make such claims.

14:42.224 --> 14:44.624
Would I have lent six million so easily?

14:45.024 --> 14:47.504
Now Wu's vanished,

14:47.663 --> 14:49.183
and you want to deny responsibility?

14:49.543 --> 14:50.783
The police?

14:51.224 --> 14:52.744
Even the courts

14:52.984 --> 14:54.104
won't side with you.

14:54.344 --> 14:54.943
Pay up.

14:55.104 --> 14:56.783
By law,

14:57.663 --> 15:00.943
Jinda Group is not
on the hook, jointly or otherwise.

15:01.303 --> 15:02.423
Similar cases

15:02.703 --> 15:05.104
with identical circumstances

15:05.543 --> 15:06.943
have already been ruled that way.

15:07.144 --> 15:08.183
You can check

15:08.504 --> 15:09.943
or consult your lawyer.

15:10.583 --> 15:11.543
Lawyer?

15:12.024 --> 15:13.423
Debts must be paid.

15:14.264 --> 15:15.144
That's natural law.

15:15.864 --> 15:16.703
Right, guys?

15:16.744 --> 15:17.663
Yes.

15:17.744 --> 15:18.583
- Right!
- Pay up!

15:18.864 --> 15:19.792
What are you doing?

15:23.183 --> 15:23.783
Don't move!

15:24.703 --> 15:25.264
Pay up!

15:25.783 --> 15:26.303
Pay up!

15:28.583 --> 15:29.583
I've told you.

15:30.943 --> 15:31.823
Don't be so rude.

15:32.384 --> 15:33.423
Rule with virtue.

15:34.783 --> 15:35.423
(Get well soon)
This is a lesson.

15:35.663 --> 15:37.024
Yes, indeed!

15:38.024 --> 15:38.744
Mr. Shen,

15:39.264 --> 15:40.583
you're so rich,

15:40.624 --> 15:41.783
swimming in cash.

15:42.024 --> 15:44.624
But we ordinary folks
have to work hard to earn.

15:44.984 --> 15:46.144
If you want to bully us,

15:46.423 --> 15:47.224
that won't be easy.

15:47.904 --> 15:48.984
We're locals here.

15:49.463 --> 15:50.904
We have plenty of time.

15:51.823 --> 15:52.624
No money today?

15:53.303 --> 15:54.423
We'll be back tomorrow.

15:54.703 --> 15:56.224
No tomorrow? Then the day after.

15:56.504 --> 15:57.823
We'll see who cracks first.

15:58.303 --> 15:59.744
I'll give you some face today.

15:59.943 --> 16:00.744
We're leaving.

16:00.984 --> 16:01.423
Let's go.

16:02.344 --> 16:02.783
Go away.

16:12.624 --> 16:13.463
Clean up.

16:13.624 --> 16:14.264
Get to work.

16:14.423 --> 16:14.943
- Back to work.
- Yes.

16:14.984 --> 16:15.744
Time to work.

16:15.943 --> 16:16.504
Begin!

16:21.624 --> 16:23.024
Let's see

16:23.144 --> 16:24.744
how a rich guy fights thugs.

16:25.744 --> 16:26.423
Right.

16:26.783 --> 16:27.984
Let him learn

16:28.183 --> 16:30.024
this water runs deeper than it looks.

16:30.183 --> 16:31.224
Wherever he came from,

16:31.344 --> 16:32.504
he'd better go back.

16:35.663 --> 16:36.144
Xu Yan.

16:36.543 --> 16:38.344
Why'd you call us here?

16:40.463 --> 16:42.183
My sister's got a startup idea,

16:42.543 --> 16:43.864
and you're all part of it.

16:45.543 --> 16:46.183
Startup?

16:50.624 --> 16:51.144
Yes.

16:52.024 --> 16:53.423
I've been thinking.

16:53.663 --> 16:56.823
We can combine our strengths.

16:57.543 --> 17:01.543
Yao can handle design
with an ethnic focus,

17:01.783 --> 17:04.104
Guan can be our brand ambassador,

17:04.663 --> 17:07.784
and my sister handles styling.

17:08.463 --> 17:10.703
Let's launch a clothing brand together.

17:11.423 --> 17:12.824
In the initial phase,

17:12.904 --> 17:17.904
we'll build exposure and our image

17:17.904 --> 17:19.344
with short videos.

17:19.784 --> 17:22.544
Later, we'll open stores

17:22.904 --> 17:24.703
and sell ready-to-wear.

17:27.864 --> 17:28.943
What do you think?

17:32.144 --> 17:32.864
Yan.

17:33.423 --> 17:35.223
It sounds great,

17:36.463 --> 17:39.943
but starting a business is tough.

17:40.743 --> 17:41.983
Take me.

17:42.344 --> 17:44.624
I poured everything
into that competition.

17:44.743 --> 17:45.423
And now?

17:46.023 --> 17:47.344
I got nothing back.

17:47.703 --> 17:48.344
Exactly.

17:48.624 --> 17:50.743
My job doesn't pay much now,

17:51.023 --> 17:51.983
but it's steady.

17:53.503 --> 17:55.064
If our business plan failed,

17:55.423 --> 17:56.344
how do we live?

17:57.824 --> 17:59.983
Besides, we lack startup fund.

18:00.344 --> 18:01.023
True.

18:04.584 --> 18:05.943
Here's my savings,

18:06.544 --> 18:07.584
150,000 yuan.

18:07.943 --> 18:09.544
This'll be our startup fund.

18:10.584 --> 18:13.183
And I'll bring in investors later.

18:13.223 --> 18:14.663
Our funds will be more than this.

18:16.344 --> 18:16.663
If...

18:17.304 --> 18:19.503
If this fails,

18:19.544 --> 18:20.743
all your money will go.

18:21.104 --> 18:22.223
Are you sure about this?

18:22.304 --> 18:23.663
I'm quite sure.

18:25.183 --> 18:26.703
This isn't impulsive.

18:29.423 --> 18:30.544
Trust me.

18:33.784 --> 18:35.223
Now I just want to ask.

18:35.344 --> 18:39.104
Are you confident in your skills?

18:40.064 --> 18:40.743
Absolutely.

18:41.104 --> 18:41.703
I've always

18:41.784 --> 18:44.904
wanted to show our ethnic clothes
to more.

18:45.064 --> 18:46.663
Mixing it with modern fashion

18:47.183 --> 18:47.904
excites me.

18:48.064 --> 18:50.023
This could be huge.

18:50.743 --> 18:52.344
My makeup skills speak for themselves.

18:52.784 --> 18:55.064
My clients posted my makeups online,

18:55.183 --> 18:56.703
and people are still copying them!

18:58.943 --> 19:01.384
Look at my face

19:01.784 --> 19:02.943
and figure.

19:04.864 --> 19:05.544
My confidence.

19:06.304 --> 19:07.544
On camera,

19:07.544 --> 19:08.423
I'm confident

19:09.183 --> 19:10.824
and photogenic.

19:11.544 --> 19:12.864
Picking me as the model?

19:13.144 --> 19:14.344
You are smart.

19:14.743 --> 19:16.423
Come on.

19:18.423 --> 19:21.864
I am good at program planning.

19:24.183 --> 19:25.083
And you have the cash.

19:28.904 --> 19:30.584
So, Yao and Guan.

19:31.344 --> 19:32.983
Any other questions?

19:34.384 --> 19:38.304
Do you need more time to consider it?

19:39.584 --> 19:40.183
Yes. I need.

19:44.864 --> 19:47.864
I need to quit my job first.

19:49.104 --> 19:50.104
Me, too.

19:51.263 --> 19:51.864
I'm free.

19:52.023 --> 19:53.064
I manage my own time.

19:53.752 --> 19:55.551
ظآزReproductions may dazzleظآز

19:55.551 --> 19:57.064
ظآزBut living uniquely outshinesظآز

19:57.064 --> 20:01.023
Then... Then let's build this.

20:01.703 --> 20:03.503
For better lives.

20:04.304 --> 20:05.064
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

20:05.304 --> 20:05.743
Cheers!

20:05.824 --> 20:06.503
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

20:07.024 --> 20:08.820
ظآزReady to shineظآز

20:08.820 --> 20:11.119
ظآزLike a raw diamondظآز

20:11.119 --> 20:12.780
ظآزConfidence shapes my styleظآز

20:12.780 --> 20:16.469
ظآزBlooming in my colors,
every frame's perfectionظآز

20:16.469 --> 20:21.289
ظآزMy beauty's defined by none
but my own commandظآز

20:32.880 --> 20:34.736
(Cultural symbolism guide)

20:38.864 --> 20:39.624
The red ones.

20:40.104 --> 20:40.943
These outfits

20:41.183 --> 20:42.064
can't be...

20:42.064 --> 20:42.703
Wait.

20:43.263 --> 20:43.983
You...

20:43.983 --> 20:45.304
We're building our own brand.

20:45.423 --> 20:46.104
There's no need.

20:46.104 --> 20:47.263
I'm just testing this sample.

20:47.263 --> 20:47.824
Last time...

20:48.983 --> 20:52.747
ظآزCherish my sweet spots,
embrace my flawsظآز

20:53.304 --> 20:54.304
Isn't that right?

20:54.304 --> 20:55.144
No.

20:55.503 --> 20:56.743
If you design it this way,

20:57.023 --> 20:58.223
when people wear it...

20:59.183 --> 21:01.223
It could work as casual wear.

21:01.223 --> 21:01.904
I hope...

21:04.096 --> 21:09.834
ظآزMy beauty's defined by none
but my own commandظآز

21:11.015 --> 21:13.020
ظآزReady to shineظآز

21:14.600 --> 21:18.192
ظآزReady to shineظآز

21:18.480 --> 21:21.209
ظآزReady to shineظآز

21:22.000 --> 21:23.632
ظآزI'm ready to shineظآز

21:29.943 --> 21:30.423
Someone!

21:30.423 --> 21:31.104
Someone liked it!

21:31.503 --> 21:32.344
Calm down.

21:32.584 --> 21:33.943
Only 41 likes?

21:35.263 --> 21:36.423
Why?

21:36.703 --> 21:37.743
Maybe at this time

21:38.423 --> 21:39.743
people aren't on their phones.

21:40.703 --> 21:41.423
Don't worry.

21:41.463 --> 21:42.423
Let's wait.

21:42.544 --> 21:43.904
It takes time.

21:46.352 --> 21:47.664
(Yan Studio:
Every thread tells a story of elegance)

21:52.104 --> 21:52.943
42 likes now!

21:55.344 --> 21:57.232
(Share the link)

21:58.288 --> 22:00.289
(Yu Yiming: True beauty lies in culture.
Please share and support!)

22:00.743 --> 22:01.584
Dr. Yu.

22:01.703 --> 22:02.584
Day off today?

22:02.784 --> 22:03.663
I'll go grab lunch.

22:04.624 --> 22:05.344
Wait.

22:06.423 --> 22:09.144
Your outfit's unique.

22:09.503 --> 22:10.663
Where'd you get it?

22:10.663 --> 22:11.304
Nice, right?

22:11.784 --> 22:12.983
A friend gave it to me.

22:13.144 --> 22:14.423
They run a clothing brand

22:14.503 --> 22:15.624
of ethnic style.

22:16.223 --> 22:18.104
This is their new sample, unisex.

22:18.263 --> 22:18.743
Ms. Wang.

22:19.223 --> 22:21.263
(Yan Studio)
You can follow their video channel,

22:21.423 --> 22:22.144
Yan Studio.

22:22.423 --> 22:22.904
Look,

22:23.463 --> 22:24.624
they post daily.

22:24.743 --> 22:25.904
Official sales coming soon.

22:27.663 --> 22:28.503
Look, their designs.

22:28.663 --> 22:29.624
Is this your girlfriend?

22:31.223 --> 22:31.824
No. It's not.

22:32.423 --> 22:33.223
Which one is she?

22:34.943 --> 22:35.663
No one is.

22:36.144 --> 22:37.616
Ms. Wang, remember to follow it.

22:45.983 --> 22:46.463
Lin.

22:47.344 --> 22:48.624
Why are you here again?

22:49.703 --> 22:50.344
For you.

22:50.904 --> 22:51.864
Why?

22:52.104 --> 22:53.503
Your mom wants you to be a manager,

22:53.503 --> 22:54.584
a bank manager.

22:54.624 --> 22:55.223
I'm not a bank.

22:55.223 --> 22:55.864
Why look for me?

22:55.983 --> 22:56.503
Lin.

22:57.263 --> 22:58.503
Last time,

22:59.064 --> 23:00.344
I only talked

23:00.624 --> 23:01.743
without any action.

23:02.544 --> 23:03.144
My bad.

23:04.624 --> 23:06.784
Now I've found you a job back home.

23:07.144 --> 23:08.784
As a receptionist
at my friend's company.

23:09.104 --> 23:10.223
Late starts, early finishes.

23:10.503 --> 23:11.533
Easy work, good earnings.

23:11.983 --> 23:12.904
Think about it

23:13.624 --> 23:14.983
and come home with me.

23:16.904 --> 23:18.344
How many times do I have to say?

23:18.584 --> 23:20.784
Breaking up with you
was my calmest decision.

23:21.064 --> 23:21.584
Lin.

23:21.983 --> 23:24.064
I'm sincerely apologizing.

23:24.584 --> 23:25.503
Come back with me.

23:25.904 --> 23:26.544
I promise,

23:26.943 --> 23:27.983
if you come back,

23:28.183 --> 23:29.023
we'll live well.

23:29.064 --> 23:30.263
No more fights. Okay?

23:30.663 --> 23:32.544
Please stop telling ghost stories.

23:33.223 --> 23:34.463
I'm not.

23:35.584 --> 23:37.423
You've only dated me your whole life.

23:38.104 --> 23:39.144
We're first loves.

23:40.023 --> 23:41.703
We've got a real foundation.

23:42.743 --> 23:44.104
When you insisted on breaking up,

23:44.743 --> 23:46.023
I didn't want it.

23:46.743 --> 23:47.864
But my parents pressured me,

23:47.904 --> 23:48.743
and you pressured me.

23:48.784 --> 23:52.423
I got panicked and agreed.

23:53.503 --> 23:54.743
Now I deeply regret it.

23:56.344 --> 23:56.904
Lin.

23:57.463 --> 23:58.384
Come back with me.

23:59.263 --> 24:00.423
Big cities are filthy,

24:00.983 --> 24:02.344
full of temptations and desires.

24:03.144 --> 24:03.983
Come back with me.

24:04.824 --> 24:05.983
I'll love you well.

24:07.223 --> 24:08.584
Whatever worries you,

24:09.784 --> 24:11.304
I'll help resolve them.

24:14.344 --> 24:15.223
Are you insane?

24:16.023 --> 24:17.104
I love big cities.

24:17.584 --> 24:18.703
I'm staying here.

24:18.743 --> 24:19.544
I'm not going back.

24:19.864 --> 24:20.463
Good!

24:21.263 --> 24:22.423
Big cities are great.

24:22.784 --> 24:23.943
They have their...

24:23.943 --> 24:24.423
Stop it!

24:25.663 --> 24:26.423
Charm.

24:27.023 --> 24:28.144
As long as you want to,

24:28.304 --> 24:29.703
I can quit my bank job.

24:29.784 --> 24:31.064
I'll go wherever you go.

24:31.144 --> 24:32.503
I'll stay and be with you.

24:33.144 --> 24:34.223
Again!

24:34.344 --> 24:35.743
What's wrong with you?

24:35.904 --> 24:36.983
We broke up!

24:36.983 --> 24:37.943
Are you even sober?

24:38.423 --> 24:39.423
I'm perfectly sober.

24:40.223 --> 24:41.743
I never wanted to break up with you.

24:42.263 --> 24:43.503
This breakup of ours

24:44.223 --> 24:47.784
was just a minor mistake.

24:48.703 --> 24:49.824
After adjustment,

24:51.943 --> 24:52.824
I believe

24:53.544 --> 24:55.064
we'll get back on track.

24:55.104 --> 24:55.943
Want me to hit you?

24:56.023 --> 24:56.423
Go on.

24:56.824 --> 24:57.463
Hit me!

24:57.983 --> 25:00.544
If hitting me brings us lasting peace,

25:01.023 --> 25:02.384
I'll endure it all.

25:04.703 --> 25:05.584
You're insane.

25:05.943 --> 25:06.904
Lin, come back with me.

25:06.904 --> 25:07.544
Let me go!

25:07.584 --> 25:07.983
Let go!

25:08.624 --> 25:09.183
What's wrong?

25:11.144 --> 25:12.064
Yu Yiming.

25:13.824 --> 25:15.064
Why are you everywhere?

25:17.824 --> 25:18.503
Perfect timing.

25:19.703 --> 25:20.663
I'm informing you here.

25:21.703 --> 25:22.344
I

25:22.864 --> 25:24.743
officially get back together
with Qiao Lin.

25:27.463 --> 25:28.023
He's insane.

25:29.983 --> 25:30.423
Lin.

25:30.904 --> 25:32.584
I'll tell you one last time.

25:32.824 --> 25:34.384
There's no future for us.

25:35.104 --> 25:35.584
Lin Tao.

25:36.584 --> 25:37.784
Qiao Lin has made up her mind.

25:37.864 --> 25:38.624
And you've seen it.

25:39.503 --> 25:39.983
Go back.

25:40.584 --> 25:41.463
Stop bothering her.

25:42.304 --> 25:42.943
Yu Yiming,

25:43.784 --> 25:45.223
you stop it.

25:45.943 --> 25:47.344
Dare you say you love Qiao Lin?

25:47.503 --> 25:49.423
Right here, right now,
in front of us both?

25:54.864 --> 25:55.663
I love her.

26:03.152 --> 26:04.208
- What did you say?
- What did you say?

26:06.743 --> 26:07.663
Say that again?

26:08.663 --> 26:09.943
You heard me clearly.

26:40.503 --> 26:41.784
Feels like ages since I saw you.

26:42.544 --> 26:43.183
Yes.

26:43.943 --> 26:46.304
Now I mainly work at my sister's place,

26:46.463 --> 26:47.943
so I have to go attend meetings.

26:48.624 --> 26:50.904
And I need to accompany
Guan to film videos.

26:52.104 --> 26:53.144
We start it from scratch,

26:53.463 --> 26:54.344
so we are quite busy.

26:55.223 --> 26:56.463
But I quite enjoy it.

26:57.864 --> 26:58.703
Good then.

26:59.824 --> 27:01.104
Whatever you do, just enjoy it.

27:07.503 --> 27:08.904
Your teacher told me

27:10.064 --> 27:11.423
you've kept up with school.

27:12.304 --> 27:13.503
Be attentive in class.

27:14.584 --> 27:15.624
Done your homework well.

27:17.584 --> 27:20.144
You've been contacting my teacher?

27:30.223 --> 27:31.304
Don't you think

27:31.423 --> 27:35.144
this outfit's pattern is too formal?

27:35.983 --> 27:36.824
The overall vibe

27:36.864 --> 27:38.263
looks so rigid.

27:38.784 --> 27:41.144
Dr. Yu brought you yogurt.

27:47.624 --> 27:48.104
Drink up.

27:57.544 --> 27:58.304
What...

27:58.423 --> 27:59.144
What's wrong?

27:59.183 --> 28:00.344
Why so gloomy?

28:01.983 --> 28:03.104
Followers increased.

28:03.144 --> 28:03.784
Increased?

28:03.824 --> 28:04.663
Let me check.

28:07.584 --> 28:08.183
We have

28:08.663 --> 28:09.503
eleven more.

28:14.624 --> 28:15.503
That's something!

28:15.743 --> 28:17.023
Better than nothing.

28:17.064 --> 28:17.463
Right?

28:18.144 --> 28:18.743
It's okay.

28:20.904 --> 28:24.144
We must admit Yan Studio has a problem.

28:28.743 --> 28:31.223
There's a British brand,

28:31.784 --> 28:33.463
Ladysee, ever heard of it?

28:35.423 --> 28:36.423
This brand

28:36.784 --> 28:40.064
focuses on medieval maiden style.

28:41.624 --> 28:45.703
The tone of the brand is elegant,

28:45.824 --> 28:46.624
exquisite,

28:46.943 --> 28:47.743
and fantasy-like.

28:48.784 --> 28:49.703
My research shows

28:51.423 --> 28:52.864
(Welcome to Ladysee's fashion realm)
the brand is niche,

28:53.064 --> 28:54.584
so the early sales were poor.

28:55.584 --> 28:57.983
But why did it later sweep Europe?

28:58.904 --> 29:01.183
During the London Olympics,

29:01.463 --> 29:03.423
it merged with a sports brand,

29:03.584 --> 29:05.904
blending classical elements

29:06.584 --> 29:09.503
and making athletic wear elegant,

29:09.743 --> 29:11.703
with girlish charm and unique style.

29:13.663 --> 29:16.144
It skyrocketed
local girls' purchasing desire.

29:19.904 --> 29:21.223
So, I was thinking

29:22.663 --> 29:24.223
if our current videos

29:24.263 --> 29:27.023
are overemphasizing ethnic styles.

29:29.344 --> 29:33.904
Our brand philosophy aims
to preserve and develop traditions.

29:34.344 --> 29:39.463
Therefore, we should make
ethnic-style clothing more appealing.

29:40.423 --> 29:46.023
We should highlight functionality
and mass appeal in our products.

29:46.423 --> 29:47.423
For example.

29:47.864 --> 29:49.344
When going on an outing,

29:50.864 --> 29:52.503
I could wear Yan Studio's clothes,

29:53.183 --> 29:55.104
feeling free and joyful.

29:55.584 --> 29:57.864
When going to work,

29:58.064 --> 29:59.983
I could also choose
Yan Studio's clothes.

30:00.344 --> 30:01.624
When going to wedding,

30:02.423 --> 30:03.023
or parties...

30:05.584 --> 30:06.544
Do you understand me?

30:07.624 --> 30:09.304
I think this direction is spot-on.

30:09.584 --> 30:11.423
If we follow Yan's suggestions,

30:11.743 --> 30:13.144
I have a preliminary concept.

30:13.463 --> 30:15.183
For our next video,

30:15.223 --> 30:19.304
could we include topics
like Normal Outfit of the Day?

30:19.584 --> 30:20.624
Normal Outfit of the Day?

30:21.904 --> 30:25.463
Then we can dial
everything down to real-life mode.

30:25.544 --> 30:27.824
So as the makeup style.

30:28.423 --> 30:32.423
Then I'll appear
more relaxed and natural

30:32.663 --> 30:33.423
during filming.

30:35.584 --> 30:36.824
No problem. Let's do this.

30:37.183 --> 30:38.743
We'll adjust and integrate it

30:39.104 --> 30:40.584
into our next collection.

30:40.584 --> 30:41.663
- Sure.
- Agreed.

30:42.824 --> 30:43.983
I'll send you the plan later.

30:44.144 --> 30:44.503
Okay.

30:44.584 --> 30:45.784
I'm going back.

30:45.864 --> 30:46.864
I'll revise the schedule.

30:47.743 --> 30:48.183
Go ahead.

30:49.144 --> 30:49.864
I'll take this.

30:52.904 --> 30:54.104
I'll see your video.

30:56.703 --> 30:57.423
(Hello, everyone!)

30:57.503 --> 30:59.503
(Welcome to today's live stream!)

30:59.663 --> 31:01.943
(Don't miss out, everyone!)

31:02.023 --> 31:03.703
(Please stay with us!)

31:03.784 --> 31:04.983
(Today, we have prepared)

31:05.023 --> 31:07.104
(amazing benefits for you.)

31:07.263 --> 31:09.423
(Including the...)

31:18.850 --> 31:20.202
(Xu Yan)

31:20.364 --> 31:23.448
(Don't forget. 8th next month
at Civil Affairs Bureau.)

31:32.624 --> 31:33.263
Mr. Shen!

31:36.304 --> 31:37.304
A batch of pipes is here.

31:37.304 --> 31:38.423
Come to inspect.

31:39.304 --> 31:39.784
Okay.

31:43.864 --> 31:45.183
You did wrong in this position.

31:45.743 --> 31:46.983
Tighten quality control here

31:47.463 --> 31:48.864
and correct this.

31:48.904 --> 31:49.263
Got it.

31:49.463 --> 31:49.824
Okay?

31:50.864 --> 31:51.544
You can leave.

31:51.624 --> 31:51.983
Okay.

31:54.544 --> 31:55.064
Hello.

31:55.784 --> 31:57.703
Mr. Shen, update you.

31:58.064 --> 31:59.423
Operations are running smoothly.

31:59.703 --> 32:00.904
How's Xu Yan doing?

32:01.584 --> 32:03.304
Yan is busy starting her business.

32:03.423 --> 32:05.064
Doesn't she livestream?

32:05.983 --> 32:07.423
She quit.

32:08.023 --> 32:11.023
Now she runs an ethnic fashion account

32:11.304 --> 32:13.023
with her sister and two others girls.

32:13.023 --> 32:13.904
How's it?

32:15.304 --> 32:16.064
Not great.

32:16.544 --> 32:17.624
A few hundred followers

32:18.304 --> 32:19.743
and under thousand likes per post.

32:20.423 --> 32:21.144
Right, Mr. Shen,

32:21.663 --> 32:23.144
Wang Defu's profile you requested

32:23.663 --> 32:25.344
was sent to your email.

32:25.344 --> 32:25.864
Got it.

32:31.144 --> 32:31.784
Bro,

32:32.064 --> 32:34.544
will Mr. Shen give us the money?

32:35.663 --> 32:36.743
If he refuses,

32:36.983 --> 32:38.144
I'll go to his father.

32:38.864 --> 32:39.423
Right.

33:16.663 --> 33:17.423
May I sit here?

33:21.223 --> 33:21.703
Sit.

33:34.864 --> 33:35.544
Shen Haoming.

33:36.023 --> 33:37.263
You're interesting.

33:38.864 --> 33:40.423
I didn't come to you today,

33:41.183 --> 33:42.503
yet you came to me.

33:43.864 --> 33:44.503
What's wrong?

33:45.104 --> 33:46.023
Can't handle it?

33:46.943 --> 33:48.023
Pay up now,

33:48.423 --> 33:49.463
principal plus interest.

33:49.663 --> 33:50.223
Make it quick.

33:51.423 --> 33:54.223
I came to you to discuss repayment.

33:55.463 --> 33:56.064
Look!

33:58.183 --> 33:58.864
Figured it out.

34:04.223 --> 34:04.784
Go ahead.

34:06.824 --> 34:08.184
We need more investment.

34:15.423 --> 34:16.344
Excuse me?

34:17.463 --> 34:19.103
We need more funds.

34:27.423 --> 34:28.423
Are you insane?

34:28.744 --> 34:31.184
You still owe me money,

34:31.664 --> 34:32.824
now you want more from me?

34:33.143 --> 34:34.463
Have you lost your mind?

34:35.304 --> 34:36.423
You want me

34:36.583 --> 34:37.904
to fall in the same trap twice?

34:38.543 --> 34:39.943
Are you taking me for a fool?

34:40.063 --> 34:41.344
Are you fooling me around?

34:45.583 --> 34:46.904
Lovely night tonight.

34:47.344 --> 34:48.143
Let's take a walk.

34:54.664 --> 34:55.304
Walk?

34:58.143 --> 34:58.623
Fine.

35:01.503 --> 35:03.543
Should we hold hands?

35:04.224 --> 35:07.103
Why don't you suggest to date?

35:14.264 --> 35:15.503
What I offer

35:16.904 --> 35:18.184
will not disappoint you.

35:20.503 --> 35:21.143
Well,

35:21.864 --> 35:23.103
people from big cities

35:23.184 --> 35:23.824
are so special.

35:27.103 --> 35:27.543
Alright.

35:28.304 --> 35:28.864
Where to?

35:38.704 --> 35:39.423
Shen Haoming.

35:41.224 --> 35:41.983
What are you doing?

35:43.063 --> 35:44.463
We're almost at my place.

35:50.704 --> 35:52.744
You said to walk with you,

35:53.344 --> 35:54.864
and I've walked with you this long.

35:55.543 --> 35:56.704
Say something.

35:59.304 --> 36:00.503
Say something!

36:00.664 --> 36:01.224
Almost there.

36:02.143 --> 36:02.664
Almost there?

36:03.824 --> 36:04.744
Let me tell you.

36:05.224 --> 36:06.143
This is my place.

36:06.304 --> 36:07.623
If you try any tricks,

36:07.744 --> 36:08.824
I'll beat you up!

36:10.103 --> 36:10.864
Ms. Wang.

36:14.344 --> 36:15.423
Haoming.

36:15.583 --> 36:16.423
What brings you here?

36:16.423 --> 36:16.943
I...

36:17.904 --> 36:18.503
Haoming.

36:18.864 --> 36:20.344
Why didn't you tell me you'd come?

36:20.344 --> 36:21.143
To surprise you.

36:21.344 --> 36:22.264
Whose car is this?

36:23.103 --> 36:23.503
Go.

36:24.423 --> 36:25.344
Go!

36:25.423 --> 36:25.943
Go.

36:26.143 --> 36:26.943
- Go.
- Go.

36:27.143 --> 36:28.023
Go.

36:28.103 --> 36:28.664
- Go.
- Go.

36:29.023 --> 36:30.583
One, two, one.

36:33.864 --> 36:34.264
Mom.

36:35.623 --> 36:36.423
Why are you here?

36:36.704 --> 36:37.344
I...

36:39.943 --> 36:40.583
Haoming.

36:41.063 --> 36:42.583
Did he cause trouble again?

36:43.103 --> 36:43.704
Tell me,

36:43.983 --> 36:44.983
I'll beat him hard!

36:45.503 --> 36:45.824
Hey.

36:45.983 --> 36:46.943
Ms. Wang.

36:47.264 --> 36:48.063
He didn't.

36:48.304 --> 36:50.583
We're discussing business nearby,

36:50.784 --> 36:51.543
so I came to you.

36:51.904 --> 36:52.943
Discussing business?

36:53.784 --> 36:54.904
Legitimate business?

36:55.543 --> 36:56.623
Of course, it's legitimate.

36:57.264 --> 36:59.623
Defu is partnering with Jinda Group.

37:02.023 --> 37:02.623
Really?

37:03.543 --> 37:04.943
Wonderful!

37:05.184 --> 37:06.304
Please come in.

37:06.344 --> 37:06.904
Please.

37:07.184 --> 37:08.143
Alright.

37:10.023 --> 37:10.864
Mind your words.

37:12.423 --> 37:14.184
Come in, Haoming.

37:14.304 --> 37:14.983
Come on in.

37:15.143 --> 37:15.623
No need.

37:15.864 --> 37:17.423
We can talk here.

37:18.704 --> 37:19.664
Alright, have a seat.

37:19.664 --> 37:20.103
Alright.

37:20.103 --> 37:21.103
I'll make some tea.

37:21.103 --> 37:21.463
No need.

37:21.543 --> 37:22.543
I'll leave soon.

37:22.744 --> 37:23.304
Don't bother.

37:23.744 --> 37:24.864
Alright, sit then.

37:26.103 --> 37:26.704
You!

37:27.384 --> 37:28.023
Talk properly.

37:34.344 --> 37:35.023
Shen Haoming.

37:36.543 --> 37:37.623
How do you know my mom?

37:38.824 --> 37:40.463
Don't be nervous.

37:41.304 --> 37:44.264
I met your mom days ago

37:44.864 --> 37:45.943
at the senior care event.

37:48.344 --> 37:50.103
You disappeared for days,

37:50.463 --> 37:51.463
so you found my mom.

37:53.463 --> 37:54.423
Listen.

37:55.344 --> 37:57.304
If you threaten me using my mom,

37:57.543 --> 37:58.784
you're asking for death.

38:00.344 --> 38:01.184
Mr. Wang,

38:02.583 --> 38:04.583
these years you've traded stocks,

38:05.184 --> 38:06.463
and run private loans,

38:07.983 --> 38:11.264
earning good money smoothly.

38:11.864 --> 38:13.864
And you got many lackeys under you.

38:15.623 --> 38:17.023
But you people

38:17.704 --> 38:20.344
are always domineering.

38:21.143 --> 38:22.744
In the neighbors' eyes,

38:23.583 --> 38:24.943
you're definitely no good people.

38:25.423 --> 38:26.824
None of your business.

38:28.704 --> 38:29.943
Despite your bad reputation,

38:30.543 --> 38:31.704
you're filial.

38:34.304 --> 38:36.184
Every year on your mom's birthday,

38:36.224 --> 38:37.784
you'd kneel to wash her feet,

38:38.543 --> 38:39.664
yet she rejects it.

38:40.304 --> 38:42.864
She would kick over the basin.

38:44.583 --> 38:47.704
Our residential project
is near the bus terminal.

38:49.184 --> 38:52.304
But the access road is still unpaved,

38:52.784 --> 38:53.864
highly inconvenient.

38:55.063 --> 38:57.224
If we can repair this road,

38:58.184 --> 39:00.664
the residents will benefit.

39:01.103 --> 39:02.864
All villagers along the road

39:02.864 --> 39:04.864
will have improved livelihoods.

39:05.304 --> 39:07.744
The town government
supports this too, right?

39:09.023 --> 39:10.184
What do you mean?

39:11.423 --> 39:14.143
Your previous investments
became bad debts.

39:15.503 --> 39:16.583
They are unrecoverable.

39:16.904 --> 39:19.264
If you invest more money

39:19.583 --> 39:20.623
for the road construction,

39:21.423 --> 39:23.583
the group will reevaluate

39:24.824 --> 39:25.744
and set up new budgets.

39:26.503 --> 39:30.304
Your lost money would
become legitimate investments.

39:30.904 --> 39:33.224
Then you can retrieve your funds.

39:33.423 --> 39:33.864
Understand?

39:34.744 --> 39:36.063
Are you fooling me around?

39:38.704 --> 39:40.224
Let's sign an agreement then.

39:41.543 --> 39:43.224
When the apartments have been completed,

39:44.264 --> 39:45.423
you can choose one first.

39:48.264 --> 39:52.184
You run a landscaping company, right?

39:54.304 --> 39:55.344
You can get

39:55.583 --> 39:58.344
all the landscaping of our project.

40:00.023 --> 40:00.864
Seriously?

40:01.224 --> 40:01.983
You know

40:03.143 --> 40:04.384
who I am, right?

40:05.304 --> 40:07.423
I keep my promise.

40:07.824 --> 40:08.744
As a native here,

40:09.023 --> 40:10.423
if you invest in road construction,

40:10.824 --> 40:12.503
it would truly

40:14.423 --> 40:17.103
benefit villagers
and bring honor to your family.

40:17.824 --> 40:19.583
Everyone will remember your name.

40:20.143 --> 40:21.864
Wang Defu.

40:23.184 --> 40:24.304
And I believe your mom

40:25.344 --> 40:27.824
will be very proud of you.

40:29.983 --> 40:33.744
I've sent all road reconstruction
contracts to your company.

40:34.543 --> 40:36.744
They include
official town government approvals.

40:38.023 --> 40:39.224
Think it over.

40:39.824 --> 40:41.983
And we'll discuss after that.

40:43.664 --> 40:44.423
It's getting late.

40:44.744 --> 40:45.543
I'm leaving.

40:49.943 --> 40:50.983
Pleasure to meet you.

40:55.704 --> 40:56.983
What did I say?

41:03.063 --> 41:04.543
Lovely night tonight.

41:06.983 --> 41:07.864
Indeed.

41:08.744 --> 41:09.943
We even held hands.

41:12.543 --> 41:13.063
You're here.

41:16.184 --> 41:16.904
Mr. Shen.

41:17.824 --> 41:18.704
What a feast!

41:19.423 --> 41:20.423
You've been here so long,

41:20.423 --> 41:21.744
yet I never hosted you properly.

41:21.824 --> 41:22.943
Now you're treating me.

41:22.983 --> 41:23.784
This makes me...

41:23.784 --> 41:24.304
Have a seat.

41:24.423 --> 41:25.423
I'm so embarrassed.

41:26.824 --> 41:27.824
I brought fine wine.

41:29.184 --> 41:30.784
We can have a drink later.

41:34.824 --> 41:36.184
Mr. Shen.

41:36.983 --> 41:39.103
After working together all this time,

41:39.264 --> 41:43.784
I see you have genuine
construction expertise.

41:44.224 --> 41:45.744
You even

41:45.904 --> 41:47.704
tamed that Wang Defu.

41:48.583 --> 41:49.623
You're young and capable.

41:50.463 --> 41:51.143
Impressive!

41:51.503 --> 41:51.943
Here.

41:52.664 --> 41:54.423
Let's have a drink.

41:55.503 --> 41:56.184
Let me toast you.

41:56.664 --> 41:57.344
Thank you.

42:01.864 --> 42:02.583
Let's eat.

42:09.304 --> 42:11.304
The group approved the budget?

42:12.344 --> 42:12.983
Yes.

42:13.784 --> 42:14.583
Really?

42:14.943 --> 42:15.864
Fantastic!

42:16.103 --> 42:16.824
Let me tell you,

42:16.864 --> 42:18.143
I've been waiting

42:18.184 --> 42:20.423
for this project to get back on track.

42:20.623 --> 42:20.983
Here.

42:21.304 --> 42:22.583
Let's celebrate. Come on.

42:24.503 --> 42:25.583
A new general manager will

42:26.063 --> 42:26.784
come tomorrow.

42:27.784 --> 42:28.423
What?

42:40.184 --> 42:43.503
This is a farewell banquet?

42:50.103 --> 42:50.983
Fire me?

42:56.543 --> 42:57.423
I can leave.

42:57.664 --> 42:58.864
I won't stay a minute longer.

42:59.344 --> 43:00.704
But remember,

43:01.143 --> 43:01.983
with me here,

43:02.664 --> 43:04.423
this mess remains contained.

43:04.704 --> 43:08.103
If I leave,
this will collapse instantly.

43:09.063 --> 43:10.184
You can't leave now.

43:10.904 --> 43:12.423
Wait until I audit the deficits,

43:12.816 --> 43:13.746
and then you can leave.

43:14.503 --> 43:15.143
What?

43:16.023 --> 43:16.824
Audit on me?

43:17.583 --> 43:18.063
Go!

43:18.224 --> 43:19.423
Let's go to the office now!

43:19.600 --> 43:20.983
I will hand over every password,

43:21.023 --> 43:21.943
every account!

43:22.543 --> 43:23.304
Let me tell you.

43:23.384 --> 43:25.023
I am completely clean.

43:25.503 --> 43:26.184
All these years,

43:26.543 --> 43:28.664
I never took an extra cent
from the company!

43:29.904 --> 43:30.904
Shen Haoming.

43:31.744 --> 43:32.664
You are outrageous.

43:38.583 --> 43:42.224
Does your brother-in-law
run a jade shop in town,

43:42.824 --> 43:43.744
selling antiques?

43:43.983 --> 43:44.503
Yes.

43:45.184 --> 43:46.904
A legitimate business
with proper licenses.

43:47.023 --> 43:47.583
What's wrong?

43:48.623 --> 43:49.143
Moreover,

43:49.184 --> 43:50.423
my brother-in-law

43:50.463 --> 43:51.503
has nothing to do with me.

43:52.623 --> 43:53.623
Including stone gambles?

43:55.463 --> 43:56.423
A stone

43:56.543 --> 43:57.704
costs tens of thousands,

43:58.464 --> 43:59.664
or even hundreds of thousands.

43:59.784 --> 44:00.344
Man!

44:00.463 --> 44:01.824
That's the gamble!

44:02.023 --> 44:02.664
Take all

44:02.704 --> 44:03.664
or lose all.

44:03.744 --> 44:04.423
What's wrong?

44:13.304 --> 44:14.983
Are they really involving
gamble on stones

44:16.023 --> 44:18.744
or transferring the kickback to you?

44:33.744 --> 44:37.824
You contracted the project
to suspicious Anqiang.

44:39.423 --> 44:42.128
Mr. Wu transferred huge kickbacks

44:42.416 --> 44:45.423
through stone gambling.

44:48.143 --> 44:50.904
You committed seriously derelict

44:51.784 --> 44:55.423
and embezzled company assets.

44:55.704 --> 44:59.023
For major embezzlement, you'll get 3

44:59.784 --> 45:01.904
to 10 years imprisonment.

45:03.943 --> 45:08.224
Massive amounts,
you'll get over 10 years imprisonment

45:08.943 --> 45:10.063
or life sentence.

45:11.704 --> 45:12.983
You know it, right?

45:16.784 --> 45:18.344
Stop racking your brains.

45:19.864 --> 45:21.184
One last chance for you.

45:22.623 --> 45:23.543
Tell me,

45:24.023 --> 45:27.704
who's protecting you in Jinda Group?

45:30.224 --> 45:33.264
You handled
the Hongyun project delay well.

45:34.744 --> 45:35.423
Chairman,

45:35.664 --> 45:38.943
all connections between
our staff and Mr. Zhang

45:40.023 --> 45:41.224
are listed here.

45:41.664 --> 45:43.583
Should I handle the follow-up?

45:44.063 --> 45:45.184
No, I'll handle it.

45:45.664 --> 45:48.720
Your divorce cooling-off period
with Xu Yan should end soon, right?

45:48.943 --> 45:50.423
When will you finalize it?

45:51.784 --> 45:52.664
8th next month.

45:53.224 --> 45:54.143
Keep it low-key.

45:54.824 --> 45:55.463
Stay discreet.

45:56.543 --> 45:57.063
Got it.

45:57.784 --> 45:58.344
I'm leaving.

46:04.847 --> 46:05.447
(People to be accused
of the project delay)

46:05.918 --> 46:07.380
(Project Manager, Zhang Youcai)

46:10.066 --> 46:12.528
(Financial staff, Wang Zhiwen, Persons
linked to Zhang Youcai, Qu Mingcheng)

46:15.280 --> 46:16.304
Qu hasn't arrived yet?

46:16.904 --> 46:17.423
Alright.

46:17.503 --> 46:18.184
Let's begin.

46:18.828 --> 46:21.851
(Persons linked to Zhang Youcai,
Qu Mingcheng)

46:32.423 --> 46:33.864
The Hongyun incident was exposed.

46:34.623 --> 46:36.463
Mr. Shen must be on high alert.

46:38.744 --> 46:42.423
Shen Haoming's marriage
is their weakness now.

46:43.904 --> 46:46.423
I heard he is getting divorced
from his wife.

46:47.023 --> 46:48.063
Investigate this.

46:48.503 --> 46:51.023
Get solid evidence of their divorce.

46:53.264 --> 46:55.180
ظآزLike fireworks that lovedظآز

46:55.180 --> 46:56.839
ظآزRushing toward the starsظآز

46:56.839 --> 46:58.898
ظآزUndaunted by painظآز

46:59.741 --> 47:01.642
ظآزFearless of flamesظآز

47:01.642 --> 47:05.296
ظآزEven if just a fleeting sparkleظآز

47:06.301 --> 47:08.125
ظآزWe shed tearsظآز

47:08.221 --> 47:11.973
ظآزDeep blue seas turn to foamظآز

47:11.973 --> 47:15.824
ظآزWe regained freedomظآز

47:15.824 --> 47:18.553
ظآزIf you remember meظآز

47:18.553 --> 47:21.392
ظآزThen I'm pleasedظآز

47:34.536 --> 47:38.680
ظآزI just wanna take my time tonightظآز

