ظآزSo I'll take my timeظآز

48:28.456 --> 48:31.624
ظآزTo reigniteظآز

48:31.624 --> 48:36.649
ظآزThe love I should deserveظآز

48:38.291 --> 48:41.297
ظآزWhen the time is rightظآز

48:41.297 --> 48:44.574
ظآزYou realizeظآز

48:44.574 --> 48:49.204
ظآزIt will all be alrightظآز

48:50.952 --> 48:55.636
ظآزCause I just have been hurt
too many timesظآز

48:57.400 --> 49:01.686
ظآزI'm giving it all to get nothing backظآز

49:03.592 --> 49:09.303
ظآزI was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even seeظآز

49:09.991 --> 49:14.491
ظآزSee the world and how it flows.
We never let goظآز

49:16.424 --> 49:19.560
ظآزSo I'll take my timeظآز

